      div(class='u-container')
        div(class='Grid')
          div(class='Grid-cell Grid-cell--4')
            h4 What is Kapla?
            p KAPLA is a construction toy made up from a set of identical elements whose proportions correspond to: 3 thicknesses for 1 width ans 5 widths for 1 length.
            p The principle is simple: each plank is placed one on top of the other, without any fixation and you just let your imagination go.
            p KAPLA is suitable for children aged 3 and up. Thanks to its simplicity and its special designed dimensions, this consruction toy enables to realise spectacular buildings or huge creations without any limits.
            p KAPLA is at once a creative, a reflection as well as a dexterity toy which gives as much joy to the small ones as adults.
            p KAPLA is used as an effective educational tool in many schools around the world.
          div(class='Grid-cell Grid-cell--8')
            img(class='u-mg--l', src='img/schema.png')
